---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy policy">
  <article class="article-prose max-w-prose">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy policy</h1>

    <p>
      Business Leaders India is a static news site. We do not require accounts, do not collect
      personal information directly, and do not run advertising trackers.
    </p>

    <h2>Hosting</h2>
    <p>
      The site is served by Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect aggregated request logs
      (IP, user agent, referer) for security and rate-limiting. See Cloudflare's privacy policy
      for details.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      If we add analytics, we will use a privacy-respecting tool that does not set tracking
      cookies. This page will be updated when that happens.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy:{' '}
      <a href="mailto:connect@publicmediasolution.com">connect@publicmediasolution.com</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
